  <trk>
    <name>Over the Albinen ladders from Leukerbad to Albinen</name>
    <desc>The oldest via ferrata in Switzerland—actually the Alps—since 1781. Traverse the adventurous Albinen ladders on the historic trade route between the villages of Albinen and Leukerbad.</desc>
